query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.openId, u.role, g.id as gestor_id, g.userId 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN gestores g ON g.userId = u.id 
WHERE u.name LIKE '%dias%' OR u.name LIKE '%fabio%' OR u.name LIKE '%fdias%' OR u.email LIKE '%dias%' OR u.email LIKE '%fabio%'
